questionsAndAnswers.question: Most Important Note for project
When can I place my order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Before placing an order, be sure to get in contact. All Work is Planned in Advance, and if you Order On my Gig Without communicating with me, i might be not able to complete your order in time and we might be face delays to start your project

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I require your Squarespace login information (username or email) or an invitation to access your Squarespace account. I Can give you my email address for this, but if you have any stuff, you must send it to me. To help us follow your design, if you have any design files, please share them with me.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you Provide Content ( Text & Images ) as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If you don't currently have any content for your website, I can create it with professional, license-free pictures, videos, and graphics together with simple, generic text. I'm not a copywriter, though! Please get in touch with a copyrighter if you require a professional copy.

questionsAndAnswers.question: what if I don't have any content and image?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Ok. Don't stress over it. I'll update your website with fictitious text and pictures. Just replace all of the material once you have it. and maybe most importantly, you can very easily customise your website.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I Get support after Order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes. I'll provide free of cost support. But it's only 15 days after the delivery project.
